<paragraph id="981DEA6AFF63FF9EFCA3E5BCFB3AFA03" blockId="6.[805,1459,1256,2008]" box="[805,1169,1430,1454]" pageId="6" pageNumber="544">from Saldanha Bay, South Africa.</paragraph>
